    "struts2_ognl_url_param": {
      "description": "Apache Struts 2 OGNL injection via URL parameter (S2-001/057/059/061 family). OGNL expression in parameter value is evaluated when the framework binds the value to a model attribute. Detect via arithmetic echo: %{1337*1338} \u2192 1788906.",
